Entries.default: "Can anybody tell me what just happened?"
"How did she come by such tremendous power at such a young age?"
"She attacked first. You saw how it went down, right? I'm not crazy."
"Gaun take you and keep you, child."
"A child... captain, what have we done?"
"She possessed the form of a child, but her mind was pure chaos. She was dead long before we found her."
"She's free now. That's all that matters, ac?"
"Cheer up, ja? Better death than whatever she was."
